X::>Does anyone have an official (or near offical) list of minor races in
 ::>and around the Imperium? I\'m trying to find as many as I can. For some
 ::>reason I have begun to develop an obsession with finding as many
 ::>official minor races!  Please help me!

 I\'m taking as "official" anything published by GDW or a GDW
 licensed source, for Traveller, Megatraveller, and TNE.  Below are
 all of the races, major and minor, that I can remember
 encountering in sources official by the above definition.  If you
 have any questions about any of them, post or email, and I\'ll try
 to get some specifics.  This list\'ll just be the names.

 Vilani         Solomani        Aslan           Hivers
 Droyne         Zhodani         Vargr           Dynchia
 Ael Yael       Bwabs           Darrians        Virushi
 K\'kree         Sabmiqys        Dolphins*       Orcas*
 Schalli*       Cymbeline Chiplife*

 The four starred names are races that I don\'t recall seeing in
 pre-TNE stuff, but in order for them to be in the state of
 development described in TNE materials, they would have had to be
 extant in the Traveller (classic - black books) era,  The
 Cymbeline Chiplife may have become extinct during the War of
 Collapse (I prefer this to "Final War", which was also used for
 the last of the Grandfather wars, which meant the "end" of the
 Ancients), except in the form of pre-Collapse Deyo transponders
 and post-Collapse Virus.
