ships are refitted.  This is especially true of weapons tech.  I suspect the
_Nagumo_ will not enjoy its advanatge for long.

There is one nit I will pick.  This designed can hardly be classified as a
High Guard design with all of these new items.  Perhaps we should call it a
TCS design instead.

