I think the would be seperate, though.  If you want to dock a ship, end the 
engine fails, you might have a problem but you probably don\'t have a
disaster.  
With a spacecraft, though, past the commitment point, though, that sucker is 
coming DOWN!!.  Maybe out where it can do it by itself is a good idea.


