Honour is but another word for Truth; percisely, Speaking the Truth,
regardless of consequences.  This is valued in the military, where you
must trust your fellow soldier with your very life.  This implies that the
Third Imp. nobility arose from a military aristocracy, like most nobility
on Earth.  The strong ties between the nobility and the Imperial Armed
forces merely underline it.

This may not have been true from Cleon to Jacquine (spell-check!): they
