powered ships landing on them. The actual danger of an accidental failure is
almost nil, but it\'s more of a problem in battle. As a result, the Alliance
Navy forbids AM powered ships from getting too close to an inhabited planet
during battle.

Although ships are hardly ever destroyed outright in battle, it\'s much easier
