Well, I never had the Hivers book, and only have the Aslan book
handy - so I can tell you what those codes mean:

ASLAN GOVERNMENTS:

G:  Small facility.  Operated by an offworld clan or controlled by a
company.  Population must be 3-.

H:  Different parts of the world are owned by several different
clans on the world.  Aslan equivalent of Balkanized.

J:  Single Clan control by an on-planet clan.  Other, smaller, non-
dominant clans may be present.

K:  Single Clan control by a Clan that controls multiple worlds.

L:  World controlled by one of the 29 Major Clans.

M:  World controlled (not owned) by a Clan that is Vassal to another
Clan.

N:  As above, but the controlling Clan is Vassal to one of the 29
Major Clans.

