arrive somewhere, I have a MINIMUM of two weeks to do whatever
I want to the locals before the "Grand Fleet" can even arrive to 
interfere.  If the locals aren\'t as big and tough as I am, they lose.  If
they are, I shouldn\'t be here, and will jump out long before the 
"Grand Fleet" arrives, so I still don\'t have to fight it...
    And the Solomani couldn\'t defend every world they owned, if 
they allocated so much of their resources to the "Grand Fleet".
