your guts was an insanely bad idea.
    If the Impies had had the resources to keep coming, they would
have kept coming.  They gave up the offensive (forever, it seems),
so they didn\'t have the power to continue.
    Note that the "they\'ll lose heart if they lose Terra" idea obviously
didn\'t work out, but the Impies never restarted the war even after 
realizing that the "logic" of their plan failed to produce demonstrable
results.  Ergo, the announced goal of the plan was a coverup for the
failure of the Impies strategy....

