Hi All,

Merry Christmas - here is a rather long scenario from my Forward
Fringe campaign. It follows two scenarios I posted to the 
short-lived Sunbane XBOAT list.

This was my first attempt to create a truly alien race. I was reading
a lot of H. P. Lovecraft and wanted to capture some of those types of
space dwelling creatures in my adventures. Though Traveller all
things are possible.

Note that it is in setext format for those of you using EasyView.

TTFN,

Glenn

